  id: 36
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i #4 \u2014 L\u1EC7nh r\xFAt lui"
  category: 5
  content: "L\u1EC6NH R\xDAT LUI \u2014 M\u1EACT. 23:00 ng\xE0y 19/3. To\xE0n b\u1ED9
    qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i r\xFAt kh\u1ECFi khu chung c\u01B0 v\xE0 c\u1EA7u v\u01B0\u1EE3t.
    L\xFD do: m\u1EA5t ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t, t\u1EF7 l\u1EC7 l\xE2y nhi\u1EC5m qu\xE1
    cao. L\u1EC7nh ph\xE1 h\u1EE7y c\u1EA7u \u0111\u1EC3 ng\u0103n l\xE2y lan sang
    b\u1EDD b\xEAn kia. K\xEDp c\xF4ng binh \u0111\xE3 g\u1EAFn charges \u1EDF tr\u1EE5
    ch\xEDnh. Bom s\u1EBD k\xEDch n\u1ED5 sau 24 gi\u1EDD. B\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 ai c\xF2n
    \u1EDF khu v\u1EF1c n\xE0y \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c xem l\xE0 \u0111\xE3 m\u1EA5t.
    Kh\xF4ng quay l\u1EA1i c\u1EE9u. K\xFD: \u0110\u1EA1i t\xE1 Morrison."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
